description: This file is the entry point for a React application. It imports React, ReactDOM, CSS styles, and the main App component. It initializes the React application and renders the App component inside the root DOM element within strict mode.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering a React application into a DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders a React component tree into the root DOM container.
